org.spongepowered.api.data.value.mutable

Interface MapValue<K,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    K - The type of the key
    V - The type of the value
    All Superinterfaces:
    BaseValue<Map<K,V>>, Value<Map<K,V>>

    public interface MapValue<K,V>
extends Value<Map<K,V>>
    Represents a specialized type of Value that is different from a CollectionValue such that the "elements" are Map.Entry. Usually, this type of value is used to represent a particular "type" of "key" that is associated to a particular "value".
